Some people claims that everyone is allowed to create art. Meanwhile, others believe that only people who are talented or optaining a special skills can create art. In my opinion, anyone can be an artist, no mater how strange it looks. I will discuss my own opinions while duiscuss the merits and the opposite.

Firstly, the main advantage to allow people to be involved in art is to exavate more talented people in the world and allow them to become who they want. For example, Oliver Tree was born in California, having a decent life but he trained and worked hard and became one of the most famous and well known artist in the planet. The inevitable loss for this society and the people is that finding a true expert artist in the world is hard. However, people who is into art can still create their art and they can have contribute to the society while enjoying themselves.

The talented-only artist opinion is a very sad consideration. Even if the tallented people will get more rewards for the art area, it also reflects the cruel fact that millions of people that wants to do art will not fulfill their wish.

In conclusion, it is better to allow people to have more opportunity on art, they can make good art, and they are prople that are determined. Art is a stage for everyone to perform, not full of tallented artists. And people arround the world can be a hidden artist.